msgid "Unable to locate TV Tunes in Kodi."
msgstr "Kan ikke finde TV melodier i Kodi."

msgctxt "#33151"
msgid "Reconnect to the same server that was previously loaded. If you want to use a different server, reset your local database, including your user information."
msgstr ""
"Forbind igen til den samme server som var indlæst tidligere. Hvis du ønsker "
"at bruge en anden server, så nulstil din lokale database, og din "
"brugerinformation."

