msgctxt "#33138"
msgid "You can update your library manually rather than rely on the server plugin Kodi Sync Queue. Launch the add-on and update libraries (or per library). To remove content, you'll need to repair the library."
msgstr ""
"Du kan opdatere dit biblotek manuelt i stedet for at afhænge af server "
"tilføjelsen Kodi Sync Queue. Åben tilføjelsen og opdatere bibloteker (eller "
"pr. biblotek). For at fjerne indhold, bliver du nødt til at reparere dit "
"biblotek."

msgctxt "#33137"
msgid "Enable Kodi Sync Queue"
msgstr "Aktivér Kodi-synkroniseringskøen"

msgctxt "#33136"
msgid "Update library"
msgstr "Opdatér bibliotek"

msgctxt "#33135"
msgid "Kodi will now restart to apply a small patch for your Kodi version."
msgstr ""
"Kodi genstarter nu for at installere en lille opdatering til din version af "
"Kodi."

msgctxt "#33134"
