msgid "Something went wrong during the sync. You'll be able to restore progress when restarting Kodi. If the problem persists, please report on the Jellyfin for Kodi forums, with your Kodi log."
msgstr ""
"Noget gik galt under synkroniseringen. Du vil kunne genskabe fremskridt når "
"Kodi genstartes. Hvis problemet fortsætter, så raporter til Jellyfin for "
"Kodi forummer, med din Kodi logfil."

msgctxt "#33118"
msgid "You've changed the playback mode. Kodi needs to be reset to apply the change, would you like to do this now?"
